<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span> ضعيف - <span class="c2">((الإرواء)</span>) <span class="c2">(٢٣٥٤)</span> , <span class="c2">((الضعيفة)</span>) <span class="c2">(٢٩٥٧ و ٦٣١٨)</span>.<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>